OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCharity's pride at         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffundraising by son of Lee  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FRigby                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A charity has praised the young son of 
OL,6, murdered soldier Lee Rigby after he    
OL,7, raised more than #50,000 for the group.
OL,9,FJack Rigby, 12, was two years old when 
OL,10,Fhis father was murdered by Islamist    
OL,11,Fextremists outside Woolwich Barracks.  
OL,13,FJack, who now lives in Halifax, West   
OL,14,FYorkshire, ran 26.2 miles in May for   
OL,15,Fcharity Scotty's Little Soldiers.      
OL,17,FIt helps children grieving the death of
OL,18,Fa parent who served in the armed       
OL,19,Fforces. Founder Nikki Scott said the   
OL,20,Fcharity was "really proud" of Jack.    
